---
/**
 * About — short, human intro grounded in the CV facts, plus a colophon for how
 * the site works. Same type system as the home/CV. The personal narrative is a
 * starting point; edit it to sound like you.
 */
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — Henry Dowd"
  description="A bit about Henry Dowd, a Pure Mathematics & Computer Science graduate of Maynooth, and how this self-hosted site is built."
>
  <article class="about">
    <a class="about__back" href="/">← Home</a>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p class="lede">
      I have a degree in Pure Mathematics and Computer Science from Maynooth; the
      infrastructure side I taught myself by running my own.
    </p>

    <p>
      The homelab behind this site started small and turned into a two-node Kubernetes
      cluster I manage entirely from a git repository: monitoring, backups, ingress, DNS,
      the lot. Most of what I know about keeping systems alive, I learned by keeping that
      one alive.
    </p>

    <p>
      I like the parts other people find tedious: making deploys boring, writing down why
      a decision was made, noticing a problem in a graph before it turns into an email.
      I'm looking for a graduate role where that's the actual job: platform, DevOps, SRE,
      or systems administration.
    </p>

    <h2>How this site works</h2>
    <p>
      This page runs as a small service on that same cluster, deployed by the same GitOps
      pipeline as everything else, and scraped by the same monitoring stack it reports on.
      It reads live metrics and recent commits over the internal network and exposes its
      own, so the platform ends up monitoring the page that describes it. The source is on
      <a href="https://github.com/hpdowd/portfolio" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .about { font-family: var(--sans); max-width: 42rem; }
  .about__back { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-soft); text-decoration: none; }
  .about__back:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .about h1 { font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 3.2rem); margin: 0.7rem 0 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .about .lede {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.6vw, 1.6rem);
    line-height: 1.45; color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .about h2 {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 2.25rem 0 1rem; padding-top: 1.75rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .about p { line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 1.1rem; }
  .about a:not(.about__back) { color: var(--accent); text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .about :focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
